<m0>Animal shelter spaying program<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS .04 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>gets boost from gifted students<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS .89 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.069 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
 <m1><styl>ruleron<ql>
